A photorealistic image of an airplane cabin interior at night during flight, viewed from a passenger's perspective in economy class. The scene shows rows of seatback screens glowing with soft blue light in the dimmed cabin. In the foreground, a fold-down tray table displays a small built-in keyboard and screen showing a document interface. Through the airplane window, stars and the dark curve of Earth's atmosphere are visible. The cabin has a futuristic yet authentic feel, with subtle purple ambient lighting along the ceiling panels and the warm glow of individual reading lights scattered throughout. USB ports and power sockets are visible on the armrest, reflecting the cabin's connectivity. The mood is contemplative and modern—a workspace suspended between continents in the quiet hours of international travel.
